all league since  scotiabank has been the official team sponsor of canadian cricket team and the title sponsor of national t championship in canada in  scotiabank was a sponsor of the world rally championships corona rally mexico in  scotiabank became the sponsor for club deportivo guadalajara chivas scotiabank has an industry partnership with the university of waterloo stratford campus since  scotiabank has been a sponsor of the ctv television networks and tsns coverage of premier league soccer and the fa cup final in  scotiabank became the official sponsor for the chilean primera división in a fiveyear period contract replacing the previous sponsor petrobras since  scotiabank is the title sponsor for the concacaf champions league tournament cultureedit in  scotiabank and cineplex entertainment partnered up to create a loyalty rewards program called scene the program allows patrons to signup for a special card that grants them points which can be redeemed for free movies or concession discounts scotiabank customers can also request a scene debit card which gives them points when used a scene visa credit card was launched in early may five cineplex entertainment locations were rebranded as scotiabank theatres in  scotiabank became the title sponsor of the nuit blanche event in toronto the sponsorship continues as of  title sponsor scotiabank giller prizecitation needed scotiabank hall of brock university in st catharines ontariocitation needed scotiabank hall in the marion mccain arts and social sciences building at dalhousie university in halifax nova scotiacitation needed in  scotiabank became the title sponsor of torontos caribana now known as the scotiabank caribbean carnival toronto extends partnership until  with the possibility of extending the partnership for another two years in  scotiabank announces partnership extension of scotiabank caribbean carnival toronto for another three years taking it to until  in  scotiabank held their first hackathon with the goal of solving canadian debt corporate social responsibilityedit the scotiabank bright future program is the banks global philanthropic vision the banks multinational reach has provided a unique opportunity to help people around the world through corporate giving and employeevolunteer programs that span across six pillars education health care social services arts and culture sports and environment in  the bank contributed  million in donations and sponsorships to community causes around the world scotiabanks employees spent  hours in  volunteering and fundraising through formal community programs scotiabanks corporate social responsibility ecoliving program encourages and facilitates environmentally preferable construction and renovation of homes the company also has internal programs related to environmental responsibility and ethical financial and lending practices recent eventsedit on october   scotiabank acquired a  stake in colpatria es colombias fifth largest bank and second largest issuer of credit cards for the tune of  billion canadian dollars in cash and stock  million shares it is the second largest foreign transaction ever by a canadian financial company overseas behind royal bank of canadas purchase in royal bank of trinidad and tobago on august   scotiabank announced that it would acquire ing direct canada for  billion the sale was completed on november   on july   scotiabank announced that it would buy citigroups retail and commercial banking operations in panama and costa rica terms of the transaction were not disclosed the purchase would increase scotiabanks client base in both countries from  to  and would add  branches to the existing  branches in both central american nations scotiabank has a strong presence in thailand through its  owned affiliate thanachart bank with the recent acquisition of siam city bank thanachart bank is now the th largest bank by assets in thailand with over  staff serving more than four million customers through  branches and  atms across the country scotiabanks former president ceo and chairman cedric ritchie died on march   he was a president of scotiabank from  and ceo and chairman from  to  he was made an officer of the order of canada for his extensive knowledge of banking and commerce in  under his leadership scotiabank expanded into more than  countries and grew to  employees awardsedit  – bank of the year – for mexico the caribbean and in jamaica by latinfinance  – bank of the year the banker magazine – london england scotiabank trinidad and tobago scotiabank belize scotiabank turks and caicos  – bank of the year the banker magazine – london england scotiabank barbados scotiabank trinidad and tobago scotiabank guyana scotiabank turks and caicos  – bank of the year the banker magazine – london england scotiabank canada scotiabank barbados scotiabank dominican republic scotiabank trinidad and tobago scotiabank turks and caicos  – bank of the year the banker magazine – london england scotiabank barbados scotiabank trinidad and tobago scotiabank turks and caicos  – best emerging market bank global finance magazine – new york scotiabank jamaica scotiabank barbados scotiabank costa rica scotiabank turks and caicos   global bank of the year the banker magazine bank of the year for the americas antigua barbados belize british virgin islands canada and turks and caicos   bank of the year in british virgin islands canada guyana jamaica and trinidad and tobago by the banker magazine  – best emerging market bank in latin america global finance magazine in jamaica barbados trinidad  tobago turks and caicos and us virgin islands unionizationedit scotiabank has unionized relationships with employees in a number of locations around the world in canada the sole unionized workplace is the domestic banking branch in deep river ontario credit agency ratingsedit senior debt credit ratings may  agency rating dbrs aa stable fitch aa stable moodys aa stable standard  poors a stable membershipedit