it services overdraft protection services locker facility foreign exchange services wealth management services loyalty programmed services cash management sme banking and cash flow forecasting services the bank offers its products and services through a network of branches digital platform third party channel atms and financial advisors the bank operates in north america asia europe the middle east and central and south america scotiabank is headquartered in toronto canada table of contents the bank of nova scotia  business analysis the bank of nova scotia  company overview the bank of nova scotia  business description the bank of nova scotia  major products and services the bank of nova scotia  analysis of key performance indicators the bank of nova scotia  five year snapshot overview of financial and operational performance indicators the bank of nova scotia  key financial performance indicators the bank of nova scotia  total income and net profit margin the bank of nova scotia  asset and liabilities the bank of nova scotia  gearing ratio the bank of nova scotia  valuation the bank of nova scotia  competitive benchmarking the bank of nova scotia  market capitalization the bank of nova scotia  efficiency the bank of nova scotia  valuation the bank of nova scotia  mergers  acquisitions and partnerships the bank of nova scotia  ma and partnerships strategy the bank of nova scotia  recent developments the bank of nova scotia  swot analysis the bank of nova scotia  swot analysis  overview the bank of nova scotia  strengths the bank of nova scotia  weaknesses the bank of nova scotia  opportunities the bank of nova scotia  threats the bank of nova scotia  company statement the bank of nova scotia  history the bank of nova scotia  key employees the bank of nova scotia  key employee biographies the bank of nova scotia  locations and subsidiaries the bank of nova scotia  head office the bank of nova scotia  other locations and subsidiaries appendix methodology ratio definit